---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import pengaturanHalaman from '../content/pengaturanHalaman/data.json';
---

<Layout title="Profil Ma'had - MTQ Tarbiyah Sunnah">
<main class="flex-grow pt-[80px]">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative w-full h-[60vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img alt="Modern mosque landscape at sunrise" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" src={pengaturanHalaman.heroProfil || "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAZ8xqf-Edcqfj6AdYWdTRkSocGXc8qRtnJc2WJFhM6T7I1LTA4hDlPDkDKxfXD7U_XQmKzW2PRCuyqS-LMWmyA4mbHJ3MXHDQN-uh89Kr95pFqS1B_mWv7cfHXGyVMLpXBI-i892-ziY4frSj8YNoWHK0OBSj7T7Wd31h1SApLaUS241S1ytEB01C2LluaqxaryNkP9rRnRH7FScjfMuBo23dNfSiCcqgitFUMO2TYfKnr_27taIzSw62llzBg0CPd2O0YfI3cRB7znA"}>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-surface/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center mt-xl">
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg md:text-display-lg text-primary mb-sm drop-shadow-sm">Membentuk Generasi Qur'ani</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-md max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Ma'had Tahfizhul Qur'an Tarbiyah Sunnah berdedikasi untuk mencetak hafizh bersanad yang berpegang teguh pada manhaj salaf, memadukan tradisi keilmuan Islam klasik dengan profesionalisme pendidikan modern.
</p>
<a href="/program/smp" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-on-secondary font-label-lg text-label-lg px-md py-sm rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] transition-shadow">Pelajari Program Kami</a>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Sejarah Section -->
<section class="py-xl px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-lg items-center bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant p-lg rounded-xl shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)]">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 rounded-xl bg-surface-variant bg-cover bg-center" style={`background-image: url('${pengaturanHalaman.gambarSejarahProfil || "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLsoN003K1-XgkIFAadcGIc_x4OqQfglK73QyUuWzQ_AoU-6NV4cND5wlnjA9OtY_zKW9HCHY93k3h6A6D9O4Rj15ZeqsnKHDkw-CzF5AdcnOSVqUU8oG5Y7Mh-6QrnwtY3qh2IVvqG35FcqE5XTVanWB38GpdjL4rpoHpvcE95vNomQ5OAdDxQ6BXAG5jaH-Oyw9tp6kSiMx_PPpZABrGccXgPojdireoBNSfu5FMn5Ia84WxPek7emIRg"}');`}>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<span class="inline-block bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-label-sm text-label-sm px-sm py-xs rounded-full mb-sm">Sejarah Kami</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg md:text-headline-lg text-primary mb-sm">Berakar pada Sunnah, Berkembang dalam Ilmu</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4">
    Berada di bawah naungan Yayasan Tarbiyah Sunnah Bandung, MTQ Tarbiyah Sunnah didirikan dengan visi menghidupkan kembali tradisi menghafal Al-Qur'an dengan tajwid dan sanad yang terhubung hingga ke Rasulullah ﷺ.
</p>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
    Perjalanan kami dimulai dari halaqah-halaqah kecil di Masjid Agung Al-Ukhuwwah, hingga kini berkembang menjadi institusi pendidikan formal berasrama yang mengkader para pemuda dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia, membekali mereka dengan ilmu syar'i yang mumpuni.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Visi Misi Section - Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-xl px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto bg-surface-container rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 islamic-pattern opacity-30"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<div class="text-center mb-lg">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg md:text-headline-lg text-primary mb-sm">Visi &amp; Misi</h2>
<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto mb-sm"></div>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">Landasan utama pergerakan dakwah dan pendidikan kami.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-md">
<!-- Visi Card -->
<div class="md:col-span-3 bg-surface-container-lowest p-lg rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-md">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-container text-3xl">visibility</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-xs">Visi Utama</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant italic">"Menjadi lembaga tahfizhul Qur'an rujukan nasional yang mencetak generasi rabbani, hafal Al-Qur'an bersanad, beraqidah lurus, berakhlak mulia, dan siap mendakwahkan sunnah di tengah umat."</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Misi Cards -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] transition-shadow">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm">menu_book</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Pendidikan Tahfizh</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Menyelenggarakan program menghafal Al-Qur'an 30 juz mutqin dengan sanad qira'ah riwayat Hafsh 'an 'Ashim.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] transition-shadow">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm">mosque</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Penanaman Aqidah</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Membekali santri dengan aqidah Ahlussunnah wal Jama'ah dan pemahaman manhaj salafush shalih yang kokoh.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] transition-shadow">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm">diversity_3</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Karakter &amp; Adab</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Membina akhlakul karimah dan kemandirian santri melalui kehidupan berasrama yang disiplin dan terpimpin.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Struktur Kepengurusan Section -->
<section class="py-xl px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="text-center mb-lg">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg md:text-headline-lg text-primary mb-sm">Struktur Kepengurusan</h2>
<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto mb-sm"></div>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">Didukung oleh tenaga pendidik yang kompeten dan berpengalaman.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-md">
<!-- Card 1 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-sm text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">person</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Ustadz Abu Haidar As-Sundawy</h4>
<p class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-secondary">Pembina</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 2 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-sm text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">school</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Ustadz Mochammad Hilman Al Fiqhy, M.A.</h4>
<p class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-secondary">Ketua Bidang Pendidikan</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 3 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(70,104,54,0.08)] flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-sm text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-xs text-lg">Ustadz Haidar Askarulqohar, Lc.</h4>
<p class="font-label-lg text-label-lg text-secondary">Mudir</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</Layout>
